OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781161488
OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon Ian Paterson
OL,4,Ccalls for inquests to take longer
OL,6,FDisgraced breast surgeon Ian Paterson
OL,7,Fsays the inquests into the deaths of
OL,8,Fhis former patients are being held too
OL,9,Ffrequently, and he has called for more
OL,10,Ftime between them.
OL,12,FThe coroner is currently investigating
OL,13,Fwhether his former patients died an
OL,14,Funnatural death because of his care
OL,15,Fand treatment.
OL,17,FThe hearings into the deaths of 63
OL,18,Fwomen began in September 2024 and were
OL,19,Fdue to finish this year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
