PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781161488
OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon Ian Paterson
OL,4,Ccalls for inquests to take longer
OL,6,FHowever, they have been beset with
OL,7,Fdelays, including being suspended
OL,8,Fwhilst there was a legal disagreement
OL,9,Fbetween parties.
OL,11,FThe total number of inquests now to be
OL,12,Fheard is 68, and the coroner is only
OL,13,Faround halfway through hearing them.
OL,15,FPaterson, who worked at hospitals
OL,16,Facross Birmingham and Solihull, has
OL,17,Fbeen given evidence to the hearings
OL,18,Fvia video link from prison, where he
OL,19,Fis serving a 20-year prison sentence
OL,20,Ffor wounding patients in the private
OL,21,Fsector.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781161488
OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon Ian Paterson
OL,4,Ccalls for inquests to take longer
OL,6,FMaking an admission to the coroner
OL,7,Ftoday at the start of the inquest into
OL,8,F29-year-old Tracey Taylor, who died in
OL,9,Fa hospice in Solihull in 1999,
OL,10,FPaterson said he is 'unable to handle
OL,11,Fmore than two inquests a month' and
OL,12,Fneeds 'at least two weeks between
OL,13,Fhearings.'
OL,15,FHe said that this is because he spends
OL,16,Fbetween 90 and 120 hours preparing for
OL,17,Feach hearing and has to balance his
OL,18,Fpreparation with prison life.
OL,20,FHe also referred to the fact that he
OL,21,Fis coming up to 70-years-old.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781161488
OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon Ian Paterson
OL,4,Ccalls for inquests to take longer
OL,6,FThe Coroner, Judge Richard Foster,
OL,7,Ftold him that he will consider what he
OL,8,Fhas said, but he is already speaking
OL,9,Fto his legal team about how best to
OL,10,Fdeal with listings in order to hear
OL,11,Fthe 68 inquests in a 'timely manner.'
OL,13,FThree inquests are due to be heard in
OL,14,FJuly.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
